#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the upper part of this control module you can see several tabs: "
"<guilabel>Focus</guilabel>, <guilabel>Titlebar Actions</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Window Actions</guilabel>, <guilabel>Movement</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Advanced</guilabel>. In the <guilabel>Focus</guilabel> panel you "
"can configure how windows gain or lose focus, &ie; become active or "
"inactive. Using <guilabel>Titlebar Actions</guilabel> and <guilabel>Window "
"Actions</guilabel> you can configure how titlebars and windows react to "
"mouse clicks. <guilabel>Movement</guilabel> allows you to configure how "
"windows move and place themselves when started. The <guilabel>Advanced</"
"guilabel> options cover some specialized options like <quote>window shading</"
"quote>."
msgstr ""
"V zgornjem delu tega nadzornega modula lahko vidite več zavihkov: "
"<guilabel>Fokus</guilabel>, <guilabel>Dejanja naslovne vrstice</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Dejanja oken</guilabel>, <guilabel>Premikanje</guilabel > in "
"<guilabel>Napredno</guilabel>. V plošči <guilabel>Fokus</guilabel> lahko "
"konfigurirate, kako okna pridobijo ali izgubijo fokus, &ie;. postanejo "
"aktivna ali neaktivna. Z uporabo <guilabel>Dejanj naslovne vrstice</"
"guilabel> in <guilabel>Dejanj oken</guilabel> lahko nastavite, kako se "
"naslovne vrstice in okna odzivajo na klike miške. <guilabel>Premikanje</"
"guilabel> vam omogoča, da nastavite, kako se okna premikajo in postavljajo "
"ob njihovem zagonu. <guilabel>Napredne</guilabel> možnosti zajemajo nekatere "
"posebne možnosti, kot je <quote>senčenje oken</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please note that the configuration in this module will not take effect if "
"you do not use &plasma;'s native window manager, &kwin;. If you do use a "
"different window manager, please refer to its documentation for how to "
"customize window behavior."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da konfiguracija v tem modulu ne bo začela veljati, če ne "
"uporabljate izvornega upravitelja oken &plasma;, &kwin;. Če uporabljate drug "
"upravljalnik oken, si oglejte njegovo dokumentacijo za prilagoditev "
"obnašanja oken."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Focus"
msgstr "Fokus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>focus</quote> of the workspace refers to the window which the "
"user is currently working on. The window with focus is often referred to as "
"the <quote>active window</quote>."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Fokus</quote> delovnega prostora se nanaša na okno, v katerem "
"uporabnik trenutno dela. Okno z fokusom se pogosto imenuje <quote>aktivno "
"okno</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Focus does not necessarily mean the window is the one at the front &mdash; "
"this is referred to as <quote>raised</quote>, and although this is "
"configured here as well, focus and raising of windows are configured "
"independently."
msgstr ""
"Fokus ne pomeni nujno, da je okno spredaj &mdash; to se imenuje "
"<quote>dvignjeno</quote>, in čeprav je to konfigurirano tudi tukaj, sta "
"fokus in dvig oken konfigurirana neodvisno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "Windows activation policy"
msgstr "Pravila aktivacije oken"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are six methods &kwin; can use to determine the current focus:"
msgstr ""
"Obstaja šest metod, ki jih &kwin; lahko uporabi za določitev trenutnega "
"fokusa:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click to focus"
msgstr "Kliknite za fokus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A window becomes active when you click into it. This behaviour is common on "
"other operating systems and likely what you want."
msgstr ""
"Okno postane aktivno, ko vanj kliknete. To vedenje je običajno v drugih "
"operacijskih sistemih in verjetno tisto, ki ga želite."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click to focus (mouse precedence)"
msgstr "Kliknite za fokus (prednost miške)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is mostly the same as <guilabel>Click to focus</guilabel>. If an active "
"window has to be chosen by the system (&eg; because the currently active one "
"was closed) the window under the mouse is the preferred candidate. Unusual, "
"but possible variant of <guilabel>Click to focus</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"To je večinoma enako kot <guilabel>Kliknite za fokus</guilabel>. Če mora "
"sistem izbrati aktivno okno (npr. ker je bilo trenutno aktivno zaprto), je "
"prednostni kandidat okno pod miško. Nenavadna, a možna različica "
"<guilabel>Kliknite za fokus</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "Focus follows mouse"
msgstr "Fokus sledi miški"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Moving the mouse pointer actively over a normal window activates it. New "
"windows such as the mini command line invoked with <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> will receive the focus, without you "
"having to point the mouse at them explicitly. &eg; windows randomly "
"appearing under the mouse will not gain the focus. Focus stealing prevention "
"takes place as usual. Think as <guilabel>Click to focus</guilabel> just "
"without having to actually click."
msgstr ""
"Aktivno premikanje kazalca miške nad običajnim oknom ga aktivira. Nova okna, "
"kot je mini ukazna vrstica, priklicana s <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo>, bodo prejela fokus, ne da bi vam bilo treba "
"izrecno usmeriti miško nanje. &npr; okna, ki se naključno pojavljajo pod "
"miško, ne bodo pridobila fokusa. Preprečevanje kraje fokusa poteka kot "
"običajno. Pomislite kot <guilabel>Kliknite za fokus</guilabel>, ne da bi "
"morali dejansko klikniti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In other window managers, this is sometimes known as <quote>Sloppy focus "
"follows mouse</quote>."
msgstr ""
"V drugih upravljalnikih oken je to včasih znano kot <quote>Površni fokus "
"sledi miški</quote>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Focus follows mouse (mouse precedence)"
msgstr "Fokus sledi miški (prednost miške)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is mostly the same as <guilabel>Focus follows mouse</guilabel>. If an "
"active window has to be chosen by the system (&eg; because the currently "
"active one was closed) the window under the mouse is the preferred "
"candidate. Choose this, if you want a hover controlled focus."
msgstr ""
"To je večinoma enako kot <guilabel>Fokus sledi miški</guilabel>. Če mora "
"sistem izbrati aktivno okno (npr. ker je bilo trenutno aktivno zaprto), je "
"prednostni kandidat okno pod miško. Izberite to, če želite fokus nadzorovati "
"z lebdenjem miške."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Focus under mouse"
msgstr "Fokus pod miško"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The window that happens to be under the mouse pointer becomes active. If the "
"mouse is not over a window (for instance, it's over the desktop wallpaper) "
"the last window that was under the mouse has focus. New windows such as the "
"mini command line invoked with <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>F2</"
"keycap></keycombo> will not receive the focus, you must move the mouse over "
"them to type."
msgstr ""
"Aktivno postane okno, ki se nahaja pod kazalcem miške. Če miška ni nad oknom "
"(na primer je nad ozadjem namizja), ima fokus zadnje okno, ki je bilo pod "
"miško. Nova okna, kot je mini ukazna vrstica, priklicana s <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo>, ne bodo prejela fokusa, za "
"tipkanje morate premakniti miško nad njimi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid "Focus strictly under mouse"
msgstr "Fokus striktno pod miško"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Similar to <guilabel>Focus under mouse</guilabel>, but even more strict with "
"its interpretation. Only the window under the mouse pointer is active. If "
"the mouse pointer is not over a window, no window has focus. New windows "
"such as the mini command line invoked with <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> will not receive the focus, you must move the "
"mouse over them to type."
msgstr ""
"Podobno kot <guilabel>Fokus pod miško</guilabel>, vendar še bolj stroga "
"interpretacija. Aktivno je samo okno pod kazalcem miške. Če kazalec miške ni "
"nad oknom, ni nobeno okno v fokusu. Nova okna, kot je mini ukazna vrstica, "
"priklicana s <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo>, "
"ne bodo prejela fokusa, za tipkanje morate premakniti miško nad njimi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that <guilabel>Focus under mouse</guilabel> and <guilabel>Focus "
"strictly under mouse</guilabel> prevent certain features, such as "
"<guilabel>Focus stealing prevention</guilabel> and the <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Alt;&Tab;</keycombo> walk-through-windows dialog, from working "
"properly."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da <guilabel>Fokus pod miško</guilabel> in <guilabel>Izostritev "
"pod miško</guilabel> preprečujeta določene funkcije, kot sta "
"<guilabel>Preprečevanje kraje fokusa</guilabel> in <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\"> &Alt;&Tab;</keycombo> pogovorno okno za sprehod skozi okna, da ne deluje "
"pravilno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delay focus by"
msgstr "Zakasnitev fokusa po"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the delay after which the window the mouse pointer is over will "
"automatically receive focus."
msgstr ""
"To je čas, po katerem bo okno, nad katerim je miškin kazalec, samodejno "
"prejelo fokus."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid "Focus stealing prevention"
msgstr "Preprečevanje kraje fokusa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option specifies how much KWin will try to prevent unwanted focus "
"stealing caused by unexpected activation of new windows."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost določa, koliko bo KWin poskušal preprečiti nezaželeno krajo "
"fokusa, ki jo povzroči nepričakovana aktivacija novih oken."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "None"
msgstr "Brez"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "Prevention is turned off and new windows always become activated."
msgstr "Preprečevanje je izklopljeno in nova okna vedno postanejo aktivirana."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Low</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Nizka</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Prevention is enabled; when some window does not have support for the "
"underlying mechanism and KWin cannot reliably decide whether to activate the "
"window or not, it will be activated. This setting may have both worse and "
"better results than the medium level, depending on the applications."
msgstr ""
"Preventiva je omogočena; ko neko okno nima podpore za osnovni mehanizem in "
"se KWin ne more zanesljivo odločiti, ali naj okno aktivira ali ne, se bo to "
"aktiviralo. Ta nastavitev ima lahko slabše ali boljše rezultate kot srednja "
"raven zakasnitve, odvisno od uporabljenih aplikacij."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Medium"
msgstr "Srrednja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "Prevention is enabled."
msgstr "Preventiva je omogočena."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "High"
msgstr "Visoka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"New windows get activated only if no window is currently active or if they "
"belong to the currently active application. This setting is probably not "
"really usable when not using mouse focus policy."
msgstr ""
"Nova okna se aktivirajo le, če trenutno ni aktivno nobeno okno ali če "
"pripadajo trenutno aktivni aplikaciji. Ta nastavitev verjetno ni zares "
"uporabna, razen če uporabljate nastavitev, da okno postane aktivno šele s "
"klikom nanj."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extreme"
msgstr "Ekstemna"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid "All windows must be explicitly activated by the user."
msgstr "Striktno za vsako okno velja, da ga lahko aktivira zgolj uporabnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Windows that are prevented from stealing focus are marked as demanding "
"attention, which by default means their taskbar entry will be highlighted. "
"This can be changed in the Notifications control module."
msgstr ""
"Okna, ki ne morejo vkrasti fokusa, so označena kot okna, ki zahtevajo "
"pozornost. Privzeto je, da to pomeni, da bo njihov prikaz v opravilni "
"vrstici označen. To lahko spremenite v Modulu za nadzor obvestil."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid "Raising windows"
msgstr "Dviganje oken"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Besides receiving focus, you can also control under which conditions windows "
"get raised, &ie; brought to the front."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega, kdaj okna prejmejo fokus, lahko nadzorujete tudi, pod katerimi "
"pogoji se okna dvignejo, &ie; prenesejo v ospredje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should make sure that at least one of the raising options is enabled, "
"otherwise windows will not be raised at all."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da je omogočena vsaj ena od možnosti dviga, sicer okna ne "
"bodo nikoli ponesena v osprednje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Click raises active window</guilabel> will bring a window to the "
"front when it is clicked on. This is enabled by default with a click to "
"focus policy."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Klik dvigne aktivno okno</guilabel> bo okno prenesel v ospredje, "
"ko nanj kliknete. To je privzeto omogočeno s tem, da okno postane v fokusu, "
"ko nanj kliknete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By activating <guilabel>Raise on hover, delayed by</guilabel> you can "
"alternatively bring a window to the front if the mouse pointer is over that "
"window for a specified period of time. You can determine the delay for this "
"option by using the spin box control. This auto-raising option is only "
"available with a hover to focus policy."
msgstr ""
"Če aktivirate <guilabel>Dvig ob lebdenju z zakasnitvijo za</guilabel>, lahko "
"postavite okno v ospredje, če je miškin kazalec določen čas nad tem oknom. "
"Zakasnitev, kdaj se okno postavi v ospredje, lahko določite z uporabo "
"vrtilnega polja. Možnost samodejnega dviga je na voljo samo z nastavitvijo, "
"da okno postane aktivno ob kliku nanj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Setting the delay too short will cause a rapid fire changing of windows, "
"which can be quite distracting. Most people will like a delay of 100-300 ms. "
"This is responsive, but it will let you slide over the corners of a window "
"on your way to your destination without bringing that window to the front."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitev prekratke zakasnitve bo povzročila hitro menjavo oken, kar je "
"lahko precej moteče. Večini ljudi je všeč zakasnitev 100-300 ms. To je "
"odzivno na vaša dejanja, vendar vam bo omogočilo drsenje čez vogale okna na "
"poti do cilja, ne da bi to okno postavili naprej."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid "Multiscreen behavior"
msgstr "Obnašanje pri večih zaslonih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This controls the behavior of window focus with multiple screens. Note that "
"these options appear only when more than one screen is currently connected."
msgstr ""
"Ta del nastavitev nadzoruje vedenje fokusa oken na več zaslonih. "
"Upoštevajte, da se te možnosti prikažejo le, če imate trenutno povezan več "
"kot en zaslon."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Separate screen focus"
msgstr "Fokus ločenih zaslonov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this option is enabled, focus operations are limited only to the active "
"screen. For instance, when you close a window, then the next window to "
"receive focus will be a window on the active screen, even if there is a more "
"recently used window on a different screen."
msgstr ""
"Ko je ta možnost omogočena, so operacije ostrenja omejene samo na aktivni "
"zaslon. Na primer ko zaprete okno, bo naslednje okno, ki bo prejelo fokus na "
"aktivnem zaslonu, tudi če je na drugem zaslonu bolj nedavno uporabljeno okno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Titlebar Actions</title>"
msgstr "<title>Dejanja naslovne vrstice</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this panel you can configure what happens to windows when a mousebutton "
"is clicked on their titlebars."
msgstr ""
"Na tej plošči lahko konfigurirate, kaj se zgodi z okni, ko kliknete gumb na "
"miški in se z miško nahajate v njihovih naslovnih vrsticah."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Titlebar Actions</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Dejanja naslovne vrstice</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section allows you to determine what happens when you double-click or "
"scroll the mouse wheel on the titlebar of a window."
msgstr ""
"Ta razdelek vam omogoča, da določite, kaj se zgodi, ko dvokliknete ali "
"pomaknete kolesce miške na naslovno vrstico nekega okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following actions are available for <guilabel>Double-click</guilabel>:"
msgstr "Za <guilabel>Dvojni klik</guilabel> so na voljo naslednja dejanja:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:325 index.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid "Maximize"
msgstr "Maksimiziraj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resizes the window to fill the height and width of the screen."
msgstr "Spremeni velikost okna, da to zapolni višino in širino zaslona."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:334 index.docbook:620
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vertically maximize"
msgstr "Navpično maksimiziraj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:336 index.docbook:622
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resizes the window to the height of the screen."
msgstr "Spremeni velikost okna, da seže do maksimalne višine ekrana."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:343 index.docbook:629
#, no-c-format
msgid "Horizontally maximize"
msgstr "Vodoravno maksimiziraj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:345 index.docbook:631
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resizes the window to the width of the screen."
msgstr "Spremeni velikost okna, da zapolni širino ekrana."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:352 index.docbook:549 index.docbook:826
#, no-c-format
msgid "Minimize"
msgstr "Minimiziraj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:354 index.docbook:551 index.docbook:828
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hides the window into its minimized state, from which it can be restored "
"&eg; via the Task Manager or Task Switcher."
msgstr ""
"Okno skrije v pomanjšano stanje, iz katerega ga je mogoče obnoviti &eg; prek "
"Upravitelja opravil ali Preklopnika opravil."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:361 index.docbook:558
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shade"
msgstr "Zasenči"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:363 index.docbook:560
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Causes the window to be reduced to simply the titlebar. Double-clicking on "
"the titlebar again restores the window to its normal size."
msgstr ""
"Povzroči, da se okno zmanjša le na naslovno vrstico. Ponovni dvoklik na "
"naslovno vrstico obnovi normalno velikost okna."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:372 index.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close"
msgstr "Zapri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:374 index.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid "Closes the window."
msgstr "Zapre okno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show on all desktops"
msgstr "Prikaži na vseh namizjih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid "Makes the window be visible on all Virtual Desktops."
msgstr "Naredi, da je okno vidno na vseh namizjih."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:390 index.docbook:479 index.docbook:588 index.docbook:863
#: index.docbook:952 index.docbook:1195
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do nothing"
msgstr "Ne naredi ničesar"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid "Nothing happens on double-click."
msgstr "Ob dvokliku se ne zgodi nič."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Mouse wheel</guilabel> can be used to trigger an action "
"depending on whether it is scrolled up or down:"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Kolešček miške</guilabel> lahko uporabite za sprožitev dejanja "
"glede na to, ali se pomaknete navzgor ali navzdol:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:407 index.docbook:880
#, no-c-format
msgid "Raise/lower"
msgstr "Dvigni/spusti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:409 index.docbook:882
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrolling up will move the window on top of other windows."
msgstr "S pomikanjem navzgor se okno premakne nad druga okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:412 index.docbook:885
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrolling down will move the window below other windows."
msgstr "Pomikanje navzdol bo premaknilo okno pod druga okna."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:419 index.docbook:892
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shade/unshade"
msgstr "Zasenči/razveljavi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:421 index.docbook:894
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrolling up will collapse the window to just its titlebar."
msgstr ""
"Če se s koleščkom pomaknete navzgor, se bo okno strnilo samo na naslovno "
"vrstico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:424 index.docbook:897
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrolling down will restore the window to its normal size."
msgstr "Če se pomaknete navzdol, boste oknu povrnili običajno velikost."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:431 index.docbook:904
#, no-c-format
msgid "Maximize/restore"
msgstr "Maksimiraj/obnovi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:433 index.docbook:906
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrolling up will maximize the window to fill the whole screen."
msgstr ""
"Če se s koleščkom miške pomaknete navzgor, bo okno povečano, da zapolni "
"celoten zaslon."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:436 index.docbook:909
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrolling down will restore it to its previous size."
msgstr "Če se pomaknete navzdol, se povrne na prejš¡njo velikost."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:443 index.docbook:916
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keep above/below"
msgstr "Ohrani zgoraj/spodaj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:445 index.docbook:918
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrolling up will make the window stay on top, covering other windows."
msgstr ""
"Če se pomaknete navzgor, bo okno ostalo na vrhu in prekrilo druga okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:448 index.docbook:921
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrolling down will make the window stay covered below other windows."
msgstr "Če se pomaknete navzdol, bo okno ostalo pokrito pod drugimi okni."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:455 index.docbook:928
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move to previous/next desktop"
msgstr "Premik na prejšnje/naslednje namizje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:457 index.docbook:930
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrolling up will move the window to the previous Virtual Desktop."
msgstr ""
"S pomikanjem navzgor se bo okno premaknilo na prejšnje virtualno namizje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:460 index.docbook:933
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrolling down will move the window to the next Virtual Desktop."
msgstr "Pomikanje navzdol bo premaknilo okno na naslednje virtualno namizje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:467 index.docbook:940
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change opacity"
msgstr "Spremeni motnost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:469 index.docbook:942
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrolling up will make the window less transparent."
msgstr "Če se pomaknete navzgor, bo okno manj pregledno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:472 index.docbook:945
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrolling down will make the window more transparent."
msgstr "Če se pomaknete navzdol, bo okno bolj pregledno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:481
#, no-c-format
msgid "Nothing happens when scrolling up or down on the window's titlebar."
msgstr "Nič se ne zgodi, ko se pomikate gor ali dol v naslovni vrstici okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can have windows automatically unshade when you simply place the mouse "
"over their shaded titlebar. Just check the <link linkend=\"advanced-unshading"
"\"><guilabel>Window unshading</guilabel></link> check box in the "
"<guilabel>Advanced</guilabel> tab of this module. This is a great way to "
"reclaim screen space when you are cutting and pasting between a lot of "
"windows, for example."
msgstr ""
"Okna lahko samodejno prenehajo biti zasenčena, če preprosto postavite miško "
"na njihovo zasenčeno naslovno vrstico. Preprosto označite potrditveno polje "
"<link linkend=\"advanced-unshading\"><guilabel>Razveljavitev senčenja oken</"
"guilabel></link> na zavihku <guilabel>Napredno</guilabel> tega modula. To je "
"odličen način za povrnitev prostora na zaslonu, ko na primer izrezujete in "
"lepite med številnimi okni."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:502
#, no-c-format
msgid "Titlebar and Frame Actions"
msgstr "Dejanja naslovne vrstice in okvirja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section allows you to determine what happens when you single click on "
"the titlebar or frame of a window. Notice that you can have different "
"actions associated with the same click depending on whether the window is "
"active or not."
msgstr ""
"Ta razdelek vam omogoča, da določite, kaj se zgodi, ko enkrat kliknete na "
"naslovno vrstico ali okvir okna. Upoštevajte, da imate lahko z istim klikom "
"povezana različna dejanja, odvisno od tega, ali je okno aktivno ali ne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each combination of mousebuttons, Active and Inactive, you can select "
"the most appropriate choice. The actions are as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Za vsako kombinacijo gumbov miške, aktivnih in neaktivnih, lahko izberete "
"najprimernejšo izbiro. Dejanja so naslednja:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:519 index.docbook:806
#, no-c-format
msgid "Raise"
msgstr "Dvigni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:521 index.docbook:808
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will bring the window to the top of the window stack. All other windows "
"which overlap with this one will be hidden <quote>below</quote> it."
msgstr ""
"Okno bo postavljeno na vrh okenskega sklada. Vsa ostala okna, ki se "
"prekrivajo s tem, bodo skrita <quote>pod</quote> njim."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:529 index.docbook:816
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lower"
msgstr "Nižje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:531 index.docbook:818
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will move this window to the bottom of the window stack. This will get the "
"window out of the way."
msgstr ""
"To okno bo premaknjeno na dno nabora oken. To bo okno odstranilo s poti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:539 index.docbook:787
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle raise and lower"
msgstr "Preklapljanje dviga in spuščanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:541 index.docbook:789
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will raise windows which are not on top, and lower windows which are "
"already on top."
msgstr ""
"To bo dvignilo okna, ki niso na vrhu, in znižalo okna, ki so že na vrhu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:578 index.docbook:853
#, no-c-format
msgid "Window menu"
msgstr "Meni okna"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:580 index.docbook:855
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will bring up a small submenu where you can choose window related commands "
"(&ie; Move to Desktop, Move to Screen, Maximize, Minimize, Close, &etc;)."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže se majhen podmeni, kjer lahko izberete ukaze, povezane z oknom "
"(&ie;. Premakni na namizje, Premakni na zaslon, Povečaj, Pomanjšaj, Zapri "
"&etc;.)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:590 index.docbook:865
#, no-c-format
msgid "Nothing happens on click."
msgstr "Ob kliku se ne zgodi nič."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid "Maximize Button Actions"
msgstr "Maksimiraj dejanja gumbov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:603
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section allows you to determine the behavior of the three mouse buttons "
"onto the maximize button."
msgstr ""
"Ta razdelek vam omogoča, da določite obnašanje treh miškinih gumbov na gumbu "
"za povečanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:613
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resizes the window to the height and width of the screen."
msgstr "Spremeni velikost okna na višino in širino zaslona."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:644
#, no-c-format
msgid "Window Actions"
msgstr "Dejanja okna"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:647
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inactive Inner Window"
msgstr "Neaktivno notranje okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:649
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This part of the module, allows you to configure what happens when you click "
"on an inactive window, with any of the three mouse buttons or use the mouse "
"wheel."
msgstr ""
"Ta del modula vam omogoča, da konfigurirate, kaj se zgodi, ko kliknete na "
"neaktivno okno s katerim koli od treh gumbov miške ali uporabite kolesce "
"miške."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:655
#, no-c-format
msgid "Your choices are as follows:"
msgstr "Vaše izbire so naslednje:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:662
#, no-c-format
msgid "Activate, raise and pass click"
msgstr "Aktiviraj, dvigni in prepusti klik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:664
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This makes the clicked window active, raises it to the top of the display, "
"and passes a mouse click to the application within the window."
msgstr ""
"To naredi okno, na katerega ste kliknili, aktivno, ga dvigne na vrh zaslona "
"in posreduje klik miške aplikaciji v oknu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:672
#, no-c-format
msgid "Activate and pass click"
msgstr "Aktiviraj in prepusti klik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:674
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This makes the clicked window active and passes a mouse click to the "
"application within the window."
msgstr ""
"S tem okno, na katerega ste kliknili, postane aktivno, klik miške pa "
"posreduje aplikaciji v oknu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:682
#, no-c-format
msgid "Activate"
msgstr "Aktiviraj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:684
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This simply makes the clicked window active. The mouse click is not passed "
"on to the application within the window."
msgstr ""
"To preprosto naredi kliknjeno okno aktivno. Klik miške se ne posreduje "
"aplikaciji znotraj okna."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:692
#, no-c-format
msgid "Activate and raise"
msgstr "Aktiviraj in dvigni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:694
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This makes the clicked window active and raises the window to the top of the "
"display. The mouse click is not passed on to the application within the "
"window."
msgstr ""
"To naredi kliknjeno okno aktivno in ga dvigne na vrh zaslona. Klik miške se "
"ne posreduje aplikaciji znotraj okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:704
#, no-c-format
msgid "Your choices for <guilabel>Mouse wheel</guilabel> are as follows:"
msgstr "Vaše možnosti za <guilabel>kolesce miške</guilabel> so naslednje:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:711
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scroll"
msgstr "Premik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:713
#, no-c-format
msgid "Just scrolls the content within the window."
msgstr "Samo premika vsebino znotraj okna."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:720
#, no-c-format
msgid "Activate and scroll"
msgstr "Aktiviraj in pomikaj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:722
#, no-c-format
msgid "This makes the clicked window active and scrolls the content."
msgstr "To naredi kliknjeno okno aktivno in pomika po vsebini."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:729
#, no-c-format
msgid "Activate, raise and scroll"
msgstr "Aktiviraj, dvigni in pomikaj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:731
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This makes the clicked window active, raises the window to the top of the "
"display, and scrolls the content."
msgstr ""
"To naredi kliknjeno okno aktivno, dvigne okno na vrh zaslona in pomika po "
"vsebini."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:743
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inner Window, Titlebar and Frame"
msgstr "Notranje okno, naslovna vrstica in okvir"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:745
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This bottom section allows you to configure additional actions when clicking "
"on a window with a modifier key pressed."
msgstr ""
"Ta spodnji del vam omogoča, da konfigurirate dodatna dejanja, ko kliknete "
"okno s pritisnjeno modifikacijsko tipko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:750
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As a <guilabel>Modifier key</guilabel>, you can select between "
"<guilabel>Meta</guilabel> (default) or <guilabel>Alt</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Kot <guilabel>Modifikatorsko tipko</guilabel> lahko izbirate med "
"<guilabel>Meta</guilabel> (privzeto) ali <guilabel>Alt</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:754
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once again, you can select different actions for <mousebutton>Left</"
"mousebutton>, <mousebutton>Middle</mousebutton> and <mousebutton>Right</"
"mousebutton> button clicks and the <guilabel>Mouse wheel</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Še enkrat lahko izberete različna dejanja za klike <mousebutton>levega</"
"mousebutton>, <mousebutton>srednjega</mousebutton> in <mousebutton>desnega</"
"mousebutton> gumba ter vrtenje <guilabel>miškinega kolesca</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:761
#, no-c-format
msgid "Your choices for the mouse buttons are:"
msgstr "Vaše izbire za gumbe miške so:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:768
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move"
msgstr "Premakni se"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:770
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allows you to drag the selected window around the workspace."
msgstr "Omogoča vlečenje izbranega okna po delovnem prostoru."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:777
#, no-c-format
msgid "Activate, raise and move"
msgstr "Aktiviraj, dvigni in premakni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:779
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This makes the clicked window active, raises it to the top of the window "
"stack, and drags the window around the workspace."
msgstr ""
"To naredi kliknjeno okno aktivno, ga dvigne na vrh okenskega sklada in "
"povleče okno po delovnem prostoru."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:797
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resize"
msgstr "Spremeni velikost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:799
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allows you to change the size of the selected window."
msgstr "Omogoča spreminjanje velikosti izbranega okna."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:835
#, no-c-format
msgid "Decrease opacity"
msgstr "Zmanjšaj motnost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:837
#, no-c-format
msgid "Makes the window more transparent."
msgstr "Naredi okno bolj pregledno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:844
#, no-c-format
msgid "Increase opacity"
msgstr "Povečaj motnost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:846
#, no-c-format
msgid "Makes the window less transparent."
msgstr "Okno naredi manj pregledno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:873
#, no-c-format
msgid "Your choices for the mouse wheel are:"
msgstr "Vaše možnosti za kolesce miške so:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:954
#, no-c-format
msgid "Nothing happens on when scrolling up or down the window's titlebar."
msgstr "Nič se ne zgodi, ko se pomikate gor ali dol po naslovni vrstici okna."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:967
#, no-c-format
msgid "Movement"
msgstr "Gibanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:969
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This page allows you to configure the <guilabel>Snap Zones</guilabel>. These "
"are like a magnetic field along the side of the screen and each window, "
"which will make windows snap alongside when moved near."
msgstr ""
"Ta stran vam omogoča, da konfigurirate <guilabel>Območja zapenjanja</"
"guilabel>. Ta so kot magnetno polje vzdolž strani zaslona in vsakega okna, "
"zaradi česar se okna zaskočijo poleg, ko jih premaknemo blizu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:978
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screen edge snap zone"
msgstr "Območje zaskočitve roba zaslona"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:980
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can set the snap zone for screen borders. Moving a window within "
"the configured distance will make it snap to the edge of the screen."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko nastavite območje zaskočitve za robove zaslona. Če premaknete "
"okno znotraj nastavljene razdalje, se bo zaskočilo na rob zaslona."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:988
#, no-c-format
msgid "Window snap zone"
msgstr "Območje zaskočitve okna"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:990
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can set the snap zone for windows. As with screen borders, moving a "
"window near to another will make it snap to the edge as if the windows were "
"magnetized."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko nastavite območje zaskočitve za okna. Tako kot pri robovih "
"zaslona se bo pri premikanju okna k drugemu okno zaskočilo na rob, kot da bi "
"bila okna magnetna."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:999
#, no-c-format
msgid "Center snap zone"
msgstr "Centralno območje zaskočitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1001
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can set the snap zone for the screen center, &ie; the "
"<quote>strength</quote> of the magnetic field which will make windows snap "
"to the center of the screen when moved near it."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko nastavite območje zaskočitve za sredino zaslona, &ie;. "
"<quote>moč</quote> magnetnega polja, zaradi katerega se okna zaskočijo na "
"sredino zaslona, ko se premaknejo blizu njega."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1010
#, no-c-format
msgid "Snap windows: Only when overlapping"
msgstr "Pripni okna: Samo pri prekrivanju"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1012
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, windows will not snap together if they are only near each other, "
"they must be overlapping, by the configured amount or less."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, se okna ne bodo zaskočila skupaj, če so zgolj "
"blizu drug drugega. Za zaskočitev se morajo prekrivati za konfigurirano "
"količino ali manj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1023
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Screen Edges</guilabel> settings module in the "
"<guilabel>Workspace Behavior</guilabel> section of the system settings, you "
"can configure windows to be quick-tiled to the whole, half, or quarter of "
"the screen when dragged near the screen edges."
msgstr ""
"V modulu z nastavitvami <guilabel>Robovi zaslona</guilabel> v razdelku "
"<guilabel>Vedenje delovnega prostora</guilabel> sistemskih nastavitev lahko "
"konfigurirate okna tako, da se hitro razporedijo po celem, polovici ali "
"četrtini zaslona ko jih povlečete blizu robov zaslona."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1031
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced"
msgstr "Napredno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1033
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Advanced</guilabel> panel you can do more advanced fine "
"tuning to the window behavior."
msgstr ""
"Na plošči <guilabel>Napredno</guilabel> lahko izvedete naprednejšo fino "
"nastavitev obnašanja oken."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1039
#, no-c-format
msgid "Window unshading"
msgstr "Odstranjevanje senčenja okna"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1043
#, no-c-format
msgid "On titlebar hover after"
msgstr "V naslovni vrstici premaknite miškin kazalec za"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1045
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is enabled, a shaded window will un-shade automatically when "
"the mouse pointer has been over the titlebar for some time. Use the spinbox "
"to configure the delay un-shading."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost omogočena, se zasenčenost okna samodejno odstrani, ko je "
"kazalec miške nekaj časa nad naslovno vrstico. Uporabite spinbox, da "
"konfigurirate zakasnitev odstranjevanja senčenja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1056
#, no-c-format
msgid "Window placement"
msgstr "Postavitev okna"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1058
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The placement policy determines where a new window will appear on the screen."
msgstr "Politika umestitve določa, kje na zaslonu se bo prikazalo novo okno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1063
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In a multi-monitor setup, the screen for windows to appear on is always the "
"active screen (that is, the screen that has the mouse pointer or the focused "
"window; see <link linkend=\"focus-multiscreen\">Multiscreen behavior</"
"link>), with the exception of windows remembering their previous position "
"(see <link linkend=\"advanced-remember-positions\">below</link>)."
msgstr ""
"Pri nastavitvi z več monitorji je zaslon, na katerem se prikažejo okna, "
"vedno aktivni zaslon (to je zaslon, na katerem je kazalec miške ali "
"fokusirano okno; glejte <link linkend=\"focus-multiscreen\">Obnašanje pri "
"več zaslonih</link>), z izjemo oken, ki si zapomnijo svoj prejšnji položaj "
"(glejte <link linkend=\"advanced-remember-positions\">spodaj</link>)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1070
#, no-c-format
msgid "Minimal Overlapping"
msgstr "Minimalno prekrivanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1072
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will place all new windows in such a manner as to overlap existing windows "
"as little as possible."
msgstr ""
"Vsa nova okna bomo postavili tako, da se bodo obstoječa okna čim manj "
"prekrivala."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1079
#, no-c-format
msgid "Maximized"
msgstr "Maksimirano"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1081
#, no-c-format
msgid "Will try to maximize all new windows to fill the whole screen."
msgstr ""
"Možnost poskusi povečati vsa nova okna do te mere, da zapolnijo celoten "
"zaslon."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1088
#, no-c-format
msgid "Random"
msgstr "Naključno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1090
#, no-c-format
msgid "Will place all new windows in random locations."
msgstr "Vsa nova okna bodo postaviljena na naključne lokacije."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1097
#, no-c-format
msgid "Centered"
msgstr "Na sredini"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1099
#, no-c-format
msgid "Will place all new windows in the center of the screen."
msgstr "Vsa nova okna bodo postavljena na sredino zaslona."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1106
#, no-c-format
msgid "In Top-Left Corner"
msgstr "V zgornjem levem kotu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will place all new windows with their top left corner in the top left corner "
"of the screen."
msgstr ""
"Postavi vsa nova okna z zgornjim levim kotom v zgornji levi kot zaslona."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1116
#, no-c-format
msgid "Under Mouse"
msgstr "Pod miško"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Will place all new windows centered under the mouse pointer."
msgstr "Vsa nova okna bodo postavljena na sredino pod kazalcem miške."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check the <guilabel>Allow apps to remember the positions of their own "
"windows</guilabel> item to open windows where they previously were rather "
"than by the placement method chosen above. Note that this remembered "
"position includes the screen assignment, so windows may open on a screen "
"other than the active one if this is where they were last located. Note also "
"that this option is only available on X11, not on Wayland, and is only "
"supported by some KDE applications."
msgstr ""
"Označite element <guilabel>Dovoli aplikacijam, da si zapomnijo položaje "
"lastnih oken</guilabel>, da odprejo okna tam, kjer so prej bila, namesto z "
"zgoraj izbranim načinom postavitve. Upoštevajte, da ta zapomnjeni položaj "
"vključuje dodelitev zaslona, zato se lahko okna odprejo na zaslonu, ki ni "
"aktiven, če so bila na tem mestu nazadnje. Upoštevajte tudi, da je ta "
"možnost na voljo samo na X11, ne na Waylandu, in jo podpirajo samo nekatere "
"aplikacije KDE."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you would like some windows to appear on specific positions, screens, or "
"Virtual Desktops, you can set up <guilabel>Window Rules</guilabel> to "
"configure special window or application settings. You can find this by right-"
"clicking on the titlebar of a window and choosing <guimenu>More Actions</"
"guimenu>, or in the <guilabel>Window Rules</guilabel> module in the "
"<guilabel>Window Management</guilabel> section of system settings."
msgstr ""
"Če želite, da se nekatera okna prikažejo na določenih položajih, zaslonih "
"ali virtualnih namizjih, lahko nastavite <guilabel>Pravila za okna</"
"guilabel>, da konfigurirate posebne nastavitve oken ali aplikacij. To "
"najdete tako, da z desno miškino tipko kliknete naslovno vrstico okna in "
"izberete <guimenu>Več dejanj</guimenu> ali v modulu <guilabel>Pravila za "
"okna</guilabel> v <guilabel>Upravljanje oken</guilabel> v razdeleku "
"sistemskih nastavitev."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1141
#, no-c-format
msgid "Special windows"
msgstr "Posebna okna"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1146
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide utility windows for inactive applications"
msgstr "Skrij pomožna okna za neaktivne aplikacije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1148
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When turned on, utility windows (tool windows, torn-off menus, ...) of "
"inactive applications will be hidden and will be shown only when the "
"application becomes active. Note that applications have to mark the windows "
"with the proper window type for this feature to work."
msgstr ""
"Ko je vklopljena, bodo pomožna okna (orodna okna, iztrgani meniji, ...) "
"neaktivnih aplikacij skrita in prikazana šele, ko aplikacija postane "
"aktivna. Upoštevajte, da morajo aplikacije označiti okna z ustrezno vrsto "
"okna, da ta funkcija deluje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Virtual Desktop behavior"
msgstr "Vedenje navideznega namizja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sometimes calling an application will activate an existing window rather "
"than opening a new window. This setting controls what should happen if that "
"activated window is located on a Virtual Desktop other than the current one."
msgstr ""
"Včasih se s klicem aplikacije aktivira obstoječe okno, namesto da se odpre "
"novo. Ta nastavitev nadzira, kaj naj se zgodi, če se to aktivirano okno "
"nahaja na navideznem namizju, ki ni trenutno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1171
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch to that Virtual Desktop"
msgstr "Preklopite na to virtualno namizje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will switch to the Virtual Desktop where the window is currently located."
msgstr "Preklopi na navidezno namizje, kjer se trenutno nahaja okno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose this option if you would like the active Virtual Desktop to "
"automatically follow windows to their assigned Virtual Desktop."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite, da aktivno navidezno namizje samodejno sledi "
"oknom na dodeljeno navidezno namizje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1183
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bring window to current Virtual Desktop"
msgstr "Prenesi okno na trenutno navidezno namizje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1185
#, no-c-format
msgid "Will cause the window to jump to the active Virtual Desktop."
msgstr "Okno bo skočilo na aktivno navidezno namizje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose this option if you would like windows to always open on the current "
"Virtual Desktop, and the active Virtual Desktop to only switch when "
"navigating there manually."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite, da se okna vedno odprejo na trenutnem "
"navideznem namizju in da se aktivno navidezno namizje preklopi samo pri "
"ročnem krmarjenju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The window stays on the desktop it currently is and the current desktop "
"doesn't change."
msgstr "Okno ostane na trenutnem namizju in trenutno namizje se ne spremeni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose this option if you would like to keep the windows and desktops as "
"they are."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite okna in namizja ohraniti takšna, kot so."

#~ msgid "Show actions menu"
#~ msgstr "Pokaži meni dejanj"

#~ msgid "Active screen follows mouse"
#~ msgstr "Aktiven zaslon sledi miški"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "When this option is enabled, the active screen (where new windows appear, "
#~ "for example) is the screen containing the mouse pointer. When disabled, "
#~ "the active screen is the screen containing the focused window."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ko je ta možnost omogočena, je aktivni zaslon (kjer se na primer "
#~ "prikažejo nova okna) tisti, ki na katerem kazalec miške. Ko možnost "
#~ "onemogočena, je aktivni zaslon ta, na katerem se nahaja okno v fokusu."
